<div class="well">
<h1>Homepage</h1>
</br>
If this is the first time on Wi-Pro.us, Welcome!
</br>
The first thing that you are going to want to do is <b><a href="/signup">Sign Up</a></b> for an account.
</br>
Once you have an account, you should go to the <b><a href="/groups">Groups</a></b> Page.  Here you will create a group to add Wi-Pros to.
</br>
After you have created a group, you must add yourself to the group on the <b><a href="/memberships">Memberships</a></b> Page.
</br>
Once you have linked yourself to the group, you can add Wi-Pros to the group.  To do this, go to the <b><a href="/wiproids">Wi-Pro Registration</a></b> Page!
</br>
The next step of this process is to <b><a href="/checkout">Checkout</a></b> a Wi-Pro.
</br>
After all of the following steps are completed, you are ready to <b><a href "/hexes">Program</a></b> a device (<a href="/devices/admin">available devices</a>)!
</br>
